built_plan = ExecutionPlanBuilder().add_path_parameter('foo', 'bar'
    ).add_path_parameter('fizz', 'buzz').add_request_interceptors(['first',
    'second']).add_request_interceptors(['third']).add_response_interceptors([
    'uno', 'dos']).add_response_interceptors(['tres']).set_handler('handler'
    ).build()
self.assertDictEqual({'foo': 'bar', 'fizz': 'buzz'}, built_plan.path_parameters
    )
self.assertListEqual(['first', 'second', 'third'], built_plan.
    request_interceptors)
self.assertListEqual(['uno', 'dos', 'tres'], built_plan.response_interceptors)
self.assertEqual('handler', built_plan.handler)
